	<Title>
		Skip flavored lip balm
	</Title>
	<Body>
		&lt;p&gt;Flavored lip balms may tempt you to lick your lips, which can aggravate chapping. To treat or prevent chapped lips, use a plain lip balm with petrolatum, beeswax or an oil-based lubricating cream. Make sure to choose one with sunscreen.&lt;/p&gt;
